reactions.description: Stereoselective epoxidation of the olefin at C6-7 in the chaetoglobosin A biosynthesis
Epoxidation of prochaetoglobosin I (chaetoglobosin V) at C6-7 to prochaetoglobosin IV
Epoxidation of cytoglobosin D at C6-7 to 20-dihydro-chaetoglobosin A
Epoxidation of chaetoglobosin J at C6-7 to chaetoglobosin A
